data.description: COMPETITIVELY PRICED!!! 4 BR, 2 1/2 Bath Colonial, with in-ground pool and 2 car garage. H/W floors in Kit., Fam. Rm., and DR. 100% new Anderson Windows and Pella storm doors (front & back) in 2005. New furnace, AC, HWH in 2015. Reinsulated perimiter walls with foam insulation in 2015. New gas stove & D/W in 2017. 100% interior repainted/redec. in 2022. Super back yard for entertaining. In-ground pool with brick paver surround; also 18 x 21 cement patio, and 18 x 25 brick patio plus 2 storage sheds. 1st floor has 1 BR with attached full bath for relative or teen
